These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, july, september
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, analyst, dancer, software-developer
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the analyst##1
2. the person driving the van is the manager##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
5. the analyst is between the person driving the trike and the person who's birthday is in june##2
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the dancer##1
7. the manager is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday        | july | september  | june | january  |
| Job         | software-developer    | analyst  | manager       | dancer     |
| Transport   | trike     | jet-ski | van       | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, drawing, magic-tricks, reading
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, tomato, lime, raspberry
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, emerald, white, ivory
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes ivory is between the person eating raspberry and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person eating raspberry is the person who likes emerald##1
6. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
7. the person eating lime is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    | reading  | magic-tricks |
| Food   | raspberry  | blueberry  | tomato   | lime    |
| Color         | emerald | ivory | coral | white      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cauliflower, pear, lettuce
4 different games are played: go, domino, mah-jongg, chess
1. the person playing domino is between the person playing chess and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left##1
6. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | lemonade   | sprite    |
| Food         | cauliflower | lettuce | cranberry | pear |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | domino        | chess      | go   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, action, romance
4 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, lizard, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person watching romance movies##2
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the owner of the hamster and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance        | fantasy   | comedy | action |
| Pet         | lizard | hamster | pony    | rat |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

