.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: tomato, peas, mango, pepper
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, comedy, disaster, family
1. the person watching family movies is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the person watching family movies is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person eating mango is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating peas##1
7. the person watching family movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person eating tomato##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Food      | tomato   | peas  | pepper | mango     |
| Movie-Genre      | comedy     | family | disaster        | satire |

