.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, scrabble, bridge
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, brazilian, australian, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, swimming
1. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the malaysian is between the british and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing billiard and the person playing scrabble##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Game    | scrabble | backgammon  | billiard | bridge      |
| Nationality   | australian  | british  | malaysian | brazilian |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | rowing | soccer     |

