.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, lavender, white, mauve
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, june, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who likes black##1
3. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes white##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes white##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Color   | white | mauve       | lavender        | black    |
| Birthday         | october | august | april  | june |

