.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, cooking, sudoku
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, domino, go
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, lettuce, asparagus, onion
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person playing bridge is between the person eating onion and the person who's hobby is camping##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
4. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | camping | cooking | board-games |
| Game   | poker  | go | bridge   | domino         |
| Food           | cranberry | asparagus  | lettuce   | onion      |

