.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, apricot, blue, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, paramedic, firefighter, writer
1. the firefighter is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes turquise##1
3. the paramedic is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the firefighter and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Color          | orange  | turquise    | blue | apricot       |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | chess  | woodworking |
| Job   | firefighter   | writer      | paramedic  | security-guard     |

