.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, pepper, pomegranate
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, iris, lily
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
3. the person eating orange is between the person eating lettuce and the person who growsrose##2
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growslily##1
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper      | pomegranate | orange | lettuce |
| Flower         | lily   | rose  | daffodil | iris |
| Sport   | soccer | lacrosse   | skiing | snowboarding |

