.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, turkish, indian, american
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, crime, satire
1. the turkish is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the turkish##1
3. the person watching epic movies is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person watching epic movies and the american##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality    | american  | indian | pakistani | turkish     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Movie-Genre     | fantasy        | satire       | epic      | crime |

