.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, orange, purple, blood-red
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, snowmobile, van, jet-ski
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes purple and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color   | blood-red | purple     | orange | black       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Transport        | jet-ski  | snowmobile      | van        | subway      |

