1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the doctor is between the fan of rock and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of dubstep is the pilot##1
5. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | hip-hop  | rock       | soul   |
| Hobby      | drawing     | hiking | filmmaking | reading |
| Job        | pilot        | doctor | police-officer     | project-manager |

