3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
5. the person who likes lilac is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the mechanic##2
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
7. the person who likes lilac is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
