.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, fishing, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, gospel, punk
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, chess, poker
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of punk##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
5. the person playing whist is between the fan of house and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person playing billiard is between the person playing poker and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Hobby   | fishing   | chess           | baking         | skydiving      |
| Music-Genre     | house | gospel | punk | country |
| Game   | chess     | whist         | billiard       | poker        |

