.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, ebony, blood-red, white
House: cape-cod, wooden, ranch-style, cottage
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the cape-cod house is the person who likes ebony##1
2. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes blood-red and the indian##2
3. the person who likes blood-red is the wooden house##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is between the ranch-style house and the mexican##2
5. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the german is between the italian and the cottage house##2
7. the cape-cod house is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Color      | ebony | blood-red | lavender   | white |
| House   | cape-cod  | wooden    | ranch-style   | cottage     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

