.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, designer, bartender, paramedic
House: townhouse, cape-cod, modern, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, swimming, weightlifting
1. the analyst is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is between the paramedic and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left of the designer##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the modern house##1
7. the bartender is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Job   | analyst    | designer | paramedic           | bartender |
| House       | townhouse | modern    | cape-cod          | palace   |
| Sport      | swimming  | rugby   | weightlifting | cricket  |

