.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, parkour, rugby, weightlifting
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, alhambra, siglo
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is swimming##2
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the siglo-smoker is between the person drinking milk and the blend-smoker##2
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | milk     | tea   |
| Sport   | swimming | weightlifting        | rugby  | parkour  |
| Cigar           | blend      | siglo         | dunhill | alhambra |

