.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
City: prague, miami, nizza, paris
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, tiparillo, pall-mall, havana
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
5. the havana-smoker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person traveling to paris and the pall-mall-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City        | paris | miami | prague | nizza |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Cigar   | davidoff | tiparillo | pall-mall | havana |

 